display_long_description:
Step into the paws of an adorable dog in Dog’s Day Out, a fun and immersive VR experience where you explore, play, and live the life of a happy pup!

**🏡 Live the Dog Life –** Roam a vibrant two-story house, explore the outdoors, and interact with a dynamic world filled with fun surprises.

**🎾 Play Mini-Games –** Fetch, dig, chase, play basketball, and even guard your home—each game rewards you with coins to spend in the shop.

**🛍️ Customize Your Pup –** Buy stylish outfits, cool watch skins, and delicious food using coins earned from mini-games.

**⏳ Manage Your Needs –** Keep an eye on hunger, energy, happiness, and hygiene bars by eating, sleeping, playing, and bathing.

**🐕 Engage with NPCs –** Annoy or befriend the character and other animals, but be careful—breaking things and mischief can cost you XP!

**🍖 Cook & Eat –** Store food in the fridge, cook meals, and enjoy quick treats to keep your pup energized.

**📋 Complete Daily Tasks –** Earn XP and level up through fun challenges, unlocking new items and mini-games.

**📺 Immersive Gameplay –** Realistic dog animations, interactive environments, and a guided tutorial make for a truly engaging VR experience.

Join Dog’s Day Out in Early Access and be part of the journey as we continue to add exciting features, improved animations, and multiplayer fun! 🐶✨
